\section{CHANGES IN VERSION 1.10.0}{

	\subsection{NEW FEATURES}{

		\itemize{

			\item \code{applyOverlap()} Apply a function on counts of a 
			\code{SummarizedExperiment} basd on the overlaps of its genome 
